biography: Enjoying my life creating good stuff at @wearecorridor ;)

latestPosts.caption:
2 days
60+ pieces of content to be posted live.
Countless memories.

PPPF wasn’t just an event; it was a full-blown creative marathon.
Live-posting, on-the-spot edits, last-minute changes, and running on instinct (and coffee). We were switching roles, swapping lenses, sharing glances that said, “You got this.”

It tested our speed, stretched our skills, and reminded us: chaos is where the best content lives.

Here’s to the madness that makes us better.
